						               													<description>&amp;#208;&amp;#151;&amp;#208;&amp;#187;&amp;#208;&amp;#190;&amp;#208;&amp;#178;&amp;#208;&amp;#181;&amp;#209;&amp;#137;&amp;#208;&amp;#184;&amp;#208;&amp;#181; &amp;#208;&amp;#191;&amp;#209;&amp;#128;&amp;#208;&amp;#184;&amp;#208;&amp;#183;&amp;#209;&amp;#128;&amp;#208;&amp;#176;&amp;#208;&amp;#186;&amp;#208;&amp;#184; (Sinister Ghosts) is a fast card game in which players have to survive during the round, escaping from ghosts.&amp;#10;Both &amp;quot;Escape&amp;quot; cards and &amp;quot;Fear&amp;quot; cards will help players survive, thanks to which players will be able to steal from rivals.&amp;#10;The main thing in this game is to stay alive at any cost! Fight with intangible monsters or run. And remember: you don't need to be the fastest, it's important that someone is slower than you.&amp;#10;During the game, players hold ghost cards, other players' fear cards, and ghost escape cards. Every turn, players must play cards and if a player plays a ghost, then he puts it in front of him, if at the beginning of the next turn he plays an escape, then he will escape from the ghost and get a winning point. The player who has escaped from the greatest number of ghosts wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
